casebody.head_matter:
In re BUI PHU XUAN, petitioner.
No. 15-8464.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 28, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of habeas corpus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
